      <title>Ares 基金成立第一年从富人手中募集了 22 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/ares-collects-2-2-billon-from-wealthy-in-first-year-of-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻看到的一份声明显示，Ares Management Corp. 已为其开放式欧洲直接贷款基金筹集了超过 22 亿欧元（22.5 亿美元），主要来自富人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/ares-collects-2-2-billon-from-wealthy-in-first-year-of-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 08:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Sam Altman 在软银活动上揭秘深度研究</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/sam-altman-unveils-deep-research-at-softbank-event-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OpenAI 首席执行官 Sam Altman 谈到了该公司的下一代人工智能代理——由其聊天机器人 ChatGPT 提供支持的深度研究。他出席了软银的一场活动，在活动上他和亿万富翁投资者孙正义宣布成立一家合资企业，为日本各地的企业开发人工智能服务。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/sam-altman-unveils-deep-research-at-softbank-event-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 08:00:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西莫雷拉·萨莱斯家族或竞购法国 Verallia</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/brazil-s-moreira-salles-family-may-bid-for-france-s-verallia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西亿万富翁莫雷拉·萨勒斯 (Moreira Salles) 家族表示，正在探索对 Verallia SA 的潜在报价，对这家法国包装公司的估值约为 36 亿欧元（37 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/brazil-s-moreira-salles-family-may-bid-for-france-s-verallia</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 06:53:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞穗银行实现创纪录目标，利润超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mizuho-profit-beats-estimates-as-bank-achieves-record-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞穗金融集团第三季度利润上涨，由于利率上升推动贷款收入增加，其提前超越了创纪录的年度盈利预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mizuho-profit-beats-estimates-as-bank-achieves-record-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 06:44:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧莱雅向制药商回售 30 亿欧元赛诺菲股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/l-oreal-to-sell-3-billion-of-sanofi-shares-back-to-drugmaker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[化妆品巨头欧莱雅公司 (L’Oreal SA) 正将所持价值 30 亿欧元（31 亿美元）的赛诺菲股份出售给这家法国制药商，在赛诺菲股价过去一年跑赢大盘后，欧莱雅将部分持股变现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/l-oreal-to-sell-3-billion-of-sanofi-shares-back-to-drugmaker</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 06:43:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度高级官员称创纪录减税将刺激经济反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/india-s-growth-slowdown-temporary-chief-economic-adviser-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级政府官员表示，印度经济增长放缓是暂时的，预算中宣布的创纪录减税措施将有助于刺激消费并改善世界第五大经济体的私人投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/india-s-growth-slowdown-temporary-chief-economic-adviser-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 04:32:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>滞胀风险导致美国国债收益率曲线自 11 月以来最趋平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/treasuries-fall-on-short-end-as-tariffs-deepen-inflation-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对主要贸易伙伴加征关税的举动可能导致经济陷入滞胀，美国国债收益率曲线创下 11 周以来的最大平缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/treasuries-fall-on-short-end-as-tariffs-deepen-inflation-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 01:14:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税引发通胀和经济增长担忧，金属价格暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/iron-ore-drops-as-trump-tariffs-raise-global-growth-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布对中国、加拿大和墨西哥征收关税，威胁爆发可能削弱全球经济增长的贸易战，铜、铝和铁矿石领跌金属价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/iron-ore-drops-as-trump-tariffs-raise-global-growth-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:57:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
